# Netlify headers — DN Airline Diagnostic Toolkit
# Security headers for all routes. NOTE: we deliberately do NOT set
# X-Frame-Options: DENY, because the scorecard must be embeddable by
# whitelisted partners. Framing is instead controlled (scoped, not "*")
# via Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors below.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), microphone=(), camera=()
  # Allow embedding only from DN + whitelisted partner domains.
  # Add each partner's production domain here before they go live.
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://*.afraa.org https://afraa.org https://*.afraa.aero;
